11. Tips, Tricks & Best Practices
🎯 Curated shortcuts and habits that save time

 Always use a Star Schema — flat tables kill performance
 Never use calculated columns where a measure works
 Use COALESCE instead of IF(ISBLANK(...))
 Keep measure tables separate from data tables
 Use VAR always — it makes debugging 10x easier
 Name your Power Query steps clearly
 Create a reference query instead of modifying source
 Use bookmarks for navigation instead of page tabs
 Add a "Last Refreshed" card to every report
